# Specification for Updates

## 1. Interviewee Dashboard Update (`components/IntervieweeDashboard.tsx`)
- **Objective:** Simplify the interface further for candidates/interviewees.
- **Visual Changes:**
  - Remove the "扫码核销" (Scan to Check-in) title text.
  - Remove the description text below the QR code ("请向现场工作人员出示...").
  - **Do NOT mask** the phone number or ID card number. Display them fully.
  - Keep the Personal Info Card (Name, Phone, ID) and the QR Code section.
  - Keep the "Success" state (Ticket Number display) as is, but ensure it remains clean.
- **Behavior:**
  - The QR code will still refresh every 60 seconds.
  - The logout button remains accessible.

